decs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459250/extras/ecfd4c257accabec5aa328060b344abb.mp4?t=1696429203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore the worlds through different terrains for ancient dig sites, tombs, temples and much more! But be careful, some places seem more inviting as they are.<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459250/extras/a1677a7bea515d8fdd175bfbb6c44721.poster.avif?t=1696429203\" width=596 height=118 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459250/extras/a1677a7bea515d8fdd175bfbb6c44721.webm?t=1696429203\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459250/extras/a1677a7bea515d8fdd175bfbb6c44721.mp4?t=1696429203\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Always make sure to stay alert when entering an ancient tomb because, for all you know, a nasty surprise may be waiting for you. Tombs may be filled with many different types of traps so always come prepared!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >More info</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459250/extras/a6d5a70836ffef6300ba043ee4603a09.webp?t=1696429203\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br>For more information check out out our website to stay up to date for new and upcoming features!",
